name: Dream Catcher Bracelet
description: Made out of hemp string, this bracelet will help you sleep better at night by keeping out your bad dreams. It can be brown or black with a gold rose bead inside. I will add more selections of beads when I run out of roses. Beaded feathers can be added also.

name: Dream Catcher
description: This Native American tradition has been passed down from generation to generation to keep away the bad dreams and only letting in the good dreams. These can be custom made, but currently the rings can only be black or metal and the net can only be white or yellow. You can pick different amounts and colors of feathers. The ring sizes are a key chain ring, a three inch ring, or a six inch ring. You can have as many feathers as you want, but you must specify with a message how many and what colors (black, gray, gray speckled, yellow, orange, brown, red, white, or pale red). If you don't specify, I'll just make one randomly.

name: Alphabet
description: You can get up to 12 letters on a bracelet, and some fillers are available such as hearts or checkered print. Only two colors can go in this bracelet, and it's about an inch wide, a little less. Send me a message specifying what you want.

name: Diagonal threes
description: There can be between six and twelve strings of any colors in this bracelet, but keep in mind that if you choose a six string bracelet, they should all be different colors for it to turn out the right way. A six string bracelet is about .5cm wide. Send a message specifying what bracelet you bought, what colors you'd like, and how big your wrist is.

name: Hearts
description: This bracelet can have two customized colors. It is only four strings, so it is about .5cm wide. The end is braided in two braids so you can tie them through the loop and onto your wrist easily. Send a message specifying what bracelet you bought, what colors you'd like, and how big your wrist is.
